<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Zoom_Viewport">Zoom Viewport</span></h2>
<p>To implement the new zoom function, a new component is available since turn.js 4.0.2 to define the viewport of the pages when zoomed in. There's an article about <a href="/docs/How_to_add_zoom_to_turn.js" title="How to add zoom to turn.js">how to add zoom to turn.js</a>.
</p>
