<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Scissors">Scissors</span></h2>
<p>Scissors is literally a scissor that cuts a page in two parts, so that you can have double pages made entirely in HTML5  and split them into two pages.
</p><p><a href="/docs/Scissor" title="Scissor">Read more about Scissor</a>
</p>
